data.description: WELCOME TO COUNTRY LIVING WHERE PEACE, PRIVACY AND TRANQUILITY PREVAIL!!!  This berm home is energy efficient and includes three bedrooms and one bath (two bedrooms do not meet  legal egress requirement).  Open floor plan in Kitchen & living room.  Great patio for enjoying summer evenings with friends and family grilling your favorite culinary delights while also enjoying local fauna and wildlife!!  The 5-acre mini farm is a Great place for horses, livestock or other farm animals with its gently rolling landscape.  A little TLC will go a long way on this great property!!  If square footage is critical buyer, and or buyers’ agent should verify.
